title: Awami League nominates Hasan Imam for Tangail-4 by-poll (Bangladesh Awami League)
text: ( Source : Bangladesh Awami League ) Published on Friday, 09 October 2015 12:44 Hits : 0 Bangladesh Awami League nominated Md Hasan Imam Khan (Sohel Hazari), former upazila chairman of Kalihati, to contest the Tangail-4 (Kalihati) by-poll
